surveyDefinition:
{
 "pages": [
  {
   "name": "Introduction",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question2",
     "html": "<b>When to File a UI Claim</b></br>\nYou should submit an application for unemployment insurance (UI) during the week your employment status has changed.  Some of those changes include:\n<ul>\n   <li>You quit or were terminated from your job</li>\n   <li>Your hours were reduced</li>\n   <li>You are temporarily or permanently laid off</li>\n</ul></br>\nNote: You will not be able to report a future separation date on the application.</br></br>\n<b>Minimum Eligibility Requirements:</b></br>\n<ul>\n   <li>You are totally or partially unemployed</li>\n   <li>You are unemployed through no fault of your own</li>\n   <li>You have worked and earned a certain amount of wages in Iowa in the last 18 months</li>\n   <ul>\n      <li>If you have worked in another state and have not worked in Iowa in the last 18 months, you must contact the unemployment office in the state(s) where you have worked</li>\n   </ul>\n   <li>You are able to work and available for work</li>\n</ul>\n</br>\n<b>Important Information You Might Need to File an Unemployment Insurance (UI) Claim</b></br>\n<ul>\n   <li>Your social security number (SSN)</li>\n   <li>Name, payroll address, work location and phone number of your last/current employer</li>\n   <li>Start and end dates of your employment</li>\n   <li>You may be asked to provide details about your employment status and ability to work</li>\n   <li>Name(s), SSN, date of birth, and relationship of any dependents that you claim on your income tax return</li>\n   <li>\n      DD-214 Certificate of Release or Discharge from Active Duty (Member Copy 4) form information, if you served in the U.S. military during the last 18 months \n      <ul>\n         <li>Note: If you do not have your DD-214 at this time, you may be required to provide it in the future</li>\n      </ul>\n   </li>\n   <li>Standard Form 8 Notice to Federal Employee about Unemployment Insurance (SF-8) or Standard Form 50 Notification of Personnel Action (SF-50), if you worked for the federal government in the last 18 months </li>\n   <li>Information about your pension, severance pay, and workers’ compensation (ex. effective date, amount, name of employer, etc.) </li>\n   <li>Your A/Alien/USCIS/I94 number and the immigration document name/type, if not a U.S. citizen </li>\n   <li>The name and local number of your labor union hiring hall </li>\n</ul>\n</br>\n<b>The Application Process </b> </br>\n<ul>\n   <li>The information you enter on this application will be saved until 11:59 p.m. on Saturday <<saturdayAfterEffectiveDate>>, if you do not submit the application today </li>\n   <li>You will be logged out of the application if there is no activity for <<initialClaimTimeoutMinutes>> minutes </li>\n   <li>It takes approximately 30 minutes to complete the application </li>\n   <li>You may be required to verify your identity during the application process </li>\n</ul></br>\n<b>After you successfully submit the application, you will: </b> </br>\n<ul>\n   <li>Be able to print a claim application summary for your records</li>\n   <li>Receive a claim confirmation number</li>\n   <li>Receive instructions for filing a weekly claim</li>\n   <li>\n      Receive a link to the UI Handbook that outlines your rights and responsibilities\n      <ul>\n         <li>\n            We recommend you review the UI Handbook before filing for UI benefits by clicking \n\t\t\there: <a style=\"color:#337ab7;text-decoration:underline;background-color:white;padding:0px !important;font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit !important;\" href=\"<<uiHandBookURL>>\" target=\"_blank\">Unemployment Insurance Handbook</a> </br>\n            The UI Handbook explains your rights and responsibilities for claiming UI benefits. It answers common questions and covers general UI information.\n         </li>\n      </ul>\n   </li>\n</ul>\n</br>\n<b>WARNING:</b> </br>\nYou may be guilty of fraud if you make false statements, provide false information, or knowingly withhold information for the purpose of receiving benefits. If you commit UI fraud, you may be fined, penalized, and criminally prosecuted. You will be required to repay UI benefits you are not eligible to receive. If you have an overpayment as a result of fraud, you will not receive UI benefits until you have paid your debt in full. </br>\n\n<a style=\"color:#337ab7;text-decoration:underline;background-color:white;padding:0px !important;font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit !important;\" href=\"<<equalOpportunityLawURL>>\" target=\"_blank\">Equal Opportunity is the Law</a>"
    }
   ],
   "title": "Introduction",
   "category": "Introduction"
  },
  {
   "name": "Citizenship confirmation",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "Citizenship confirmation",
     "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
     "title": {
      "default": "Are you a citizen of the United States?",
      "es": "[ES] Are you a citizen of the United States?"
     },
     "isRequired": true,
     "choices": [
      "Yes",
      "No"
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "panel",
     "name": "notACitizenPanel",
     "elements": [
      {
       "type": "checkbox",
       "name": "Non-citizen work documents",
       "tag": "Optimum Checkbox",
       "title": {
        "default": "Please select the document that confirms you are approved to work in the United States.",
        "es": "[ES] Please select the document that confirms you are approved to work in the United States."
       },
       "isRequired": true,
       "choices": [
        {
         "value": "Permanent Resident Card I-551",
         "text": {
          "es": "Permanent Resident Card I-551"
         }
        },
        {
         "value": "Employment Authorization Document Form I-766",
         "text": {
          "es": "Employment Authorization Document Form I-766"
         }
        },
        {
         "value": "Arrival Departure Record Form I-94",
         "text": {
          "es": "Arrival Departure Record Form I-94"
         }
        },
        {
         "value": "Refugee Travel Document Form I-571",
         "text": {
          "es": "Refugee Travel Document Form I-571"
         }
        },
        {
         "value": "Reentry Permit Form I-327",
         "text": {
          "es": "Reentry Permit Form I-327"
         }
        },
        {
         "value": "Other",
         "text": {
          "es": "Other"
         }
        }
       ]
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "html",
         "name": "question22",
         "html": {
          "default": "Permanent Resident Card I-551",
          "es": "[ES] Permanent Resident Card I-551"
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Permanent Resident Card I-551 Follow Up 1/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": {
          "default": "Alien/USCIS Number",
          "es": "[ES] Alien/USCIS Number"
         },
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Permanent Resident Card I-551 Follow Up 2/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": {
          "default": "Card Number",
          "es": "[ES] Card Number"
         },
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Permanent Resident Card I-551 Follow Up 3/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Date",
         "title": {
          "default": "Document Expiration Date",
          "es": "[ES] Document Expiration Date"
         },
         "isRequired": true
        }
       ],
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Non-citizen work documents} contains 'Permanent Resident Card I-551'"
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel4",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "html",
         "name": "question23",
         "html": "Employment Authorization Document Form I-766"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Employment Authorization Document Form I-766 Follow Up 1/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": "Alien/USCIS Number",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Employment Authorization Document Form I-766 Follow Up 2/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": "Card Number",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Employment Authorization Document Form I-766 Follow Up 3/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Date",
         "title": "Document Expiration Date",
         "isRequired": true
        }
       ],
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Non-citizen work documents} contains 'Employment Authorization Document Form I-766'"
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel2",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "html",
         "name": "question24",
         "html": "Arrival Departure Record Form I-94"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Arrival Departure Record Form I-94 Follow Up 1/2",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": "I-94 Number",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Arrival Departure Record Form I-94 Follow Up 2/2",
         "tag": "Optimum Date",
         "title": "Document Expiration Date",
         "isRequired": true
        }
       ],
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Non-citizen work documents} contains 'Arrival Departure Record Form I-94'"
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel2",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "html",
         "name": "question25",
         "html": "Refugee Travel Document Form I-571"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Refugee Travel Document Form I-571 Follow Up 1/2",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": "Alien/USCIS Number",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Refugee Travel Document Form I-571 Follow Up 2/2",
         "tag": "Optimum Date",
         "title": "Document Expiration Date",
         "isRequired": true
        }
       ],
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Non-citizen work documents} contains 'Refugee Travel Document Form I-571'"
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel3",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "html",
         "name": "question26",
         "html": "Reentry Permit Form I-327"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Reentry Permit Form I-327 1/2",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": "Alien/USCIS Number",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Reentry Permit Form I-327 Follow Up 2/2",
         "tag": "Optimum Date",
         "title": "Document Expiration Date",
         "isRequired": true
        }
       ],
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Non-citizen work documents} contains 'Reentry Permit Form I-327'"
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel1",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "html",
         "name": "question27",
         "html": "Other"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Other Follow Up 1/3",
         "tag": "Optimum SingleLine",
         "title": "Document Name",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Other Follow Up 2/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": "Alien/USCIS Number ",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Other Follow Up 3/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Date",
         "title": "Document Expiration Date",
         "isRequired": true
        }
       ],
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Non-citizen work documents} contains 'Other'"
      }
     ],
     "visible": false,
     "visibleIf": "{Citizenship confirmation} = 'No'"
    }
   ],
   "title": "Citizenship confirmation",
   "category": "Citizenship confirmation"
  },
  {
   "name": "General Questions",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "Out of state wages 1",
     "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
     "title": "Have you filed for unemployment insurance benefits in any state other than Iowa since <<basePeriodBeginDate>>? ",
     "isRequired": true,
     "choices": [
      "Yes",
      "No"
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "info",
     "visible": false,
     "visibleIf": "{Out of state wages 1} = 'Yes'",
     "html": "If you have benefits available on an existing claim in another state, you must contact that state."
    }
   ],
   "title": "General Questions",
   "category": "General Questions",
   "blockIf": "{Out of state wages 1} = 'Yes'"
  },
  {
   "name": "Union Hiring Hall",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "Union hiring hall",
     "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
     "title": "Do you receive work through a union hiring hall?",
     "description": "An employment office operated by a union for placing members in jobs.",
     "isRequired": true,
     "choices": [
      "Yes",
      "No"
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "panel",
     "name": "panel5",
     "elements": [
      {
       "type": "radiogroup",
       "name": "Union standing",
       "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
       "title": "Are you a member in good standing?",
       "isRequired": true,
       "choices": [
        "Yes",
        "No"
       ]
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel6",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Union name",
         "tag": "Optimum SingleLine",
         "title": "Please enter your union name",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Union local number",
         "tag": "Optimum Number",
         "title": "Please enter your union local number",
         "isRequired": true
        }
       ],
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Union standing}='Yes'"
      }
     ],
     "visible": false,
     "visibleIf": "{Union hiring hall}='Yes'"
    }
   ],
   "title": "Union Hiring Hall",
   "category": "Union Hiring Hall"
  },
  {
   "name": "Out Of State Employment",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "Out of state wages 2",
     "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
     "title": "Have you worked in any state(s) other than Iowa since <<basePeriodBeginDate>>?",
     "isRequired": true,
     "choices": [
      "Yes",
      "No"
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question5",
     "visible": false,
     "visibleIf": "{Out of state wages 2} = 'Yes'",
     "html": "TODO: use multi select for multiple states."
    },
    {
     "type": "checkbox",
     "name": "Other states worked in",
     "visible": false,
     "visibleIf": "{Out of state wages 2} = 'Yes'",
     "tag": "Optimum Checkbox",
     "title": "Select all states where you worked since <<basePeriodBeginDate>>",
     "isRequired": true,
     "choices": [
      "item1",
      "item2",
      "item3"
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "Other states wages 1?",
     "visible": false,
     "visibleIf": "{Out of state wages 2}='Yes'",
     "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
     "title": "Wages earned in other states may be added to your Iowa claim to satisfy the wage qualification requirements or to increase your benefit amount. Do you want out of state wages added to your Iowa claim",
     "isRequired": true,
     "choices": [
      "Yes",
      "No"
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question4",
     "visible": false,
     "visibleIf": "{Other states wages 1?} = 'Yes'",
     "html": "Wages you earned in other states will not be listed on your first monetary because these wages must be requested from the other state(s). Once we receive your wages, we will send you a corrected monetary record."
    }
   ],
   "title": "Out Of State Employment",
   "category": "Out Of State Employment",
   "blockIf": "{Other states wages 1?} = 'Yes'"
  },
  {
   "name": "Military Service",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "Military service",
     "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
     "title": "Were you a member of the U.S. military on active duty at any time since <<basePeriodBeginDate>>?",
     "isRequired": true,
     "choices": [
      "Yes",
      "No"
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "panel",
     "name": "panel7",
     "elements": [
      {
       "type": "dropdown",
       "name": "Where are you?",
       "tag": "Optimum Dropdown",
       "title": "What state are you physically located in at this moment?",
       "isRequired": true,
       "choiceUrl": "/optimum-clientside-library/platform-services/dist/data/statesList.json"
      },
      {
       "type": "html",
       "name": "Military service Msg",
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Where are you?} notempty and {Where are you?} != 'IA'",
       "html": "When filing a military unemployment claim, federal law requires you to be physically present in the state in which you are filing. You must file the application in the state where you are currently located. "
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel8",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "html",
         "name": "question1",
         "html": "Additional information is needed to complete your claim. Use your Certificate of Release or Discharge from Active Duty DD214 to answer the following questions then upload your Member 4 copy of the DD214."
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Military details 1/11",
         "tag": "Optimum SingleLine",
         "title": "What was your Branch of Service? (Item 2)",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Military details 2/11",
         "tag": "Optimum SingleLine",
         "title": "What was your last pay grade? (Item 4b)",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Military details 3/11",
         "tag": "Optimum Date",
         "title": "What was your Entry Date? (Item 12a)",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "name": "Militarydetails4/11",
         "tag": "Optimum Date",
         "title": "What was your Separation Date? (Item 12b)",
         "isRequired": true
        },
        {
         "type": "html",
         "name": "Military can't submit msg",
         "visible": false,
         "visibleIf": "compareDate({Militarydetails4/11}, computeBYB()) = 1",
         "html": "If you submit this application today, the start date of your UI claim is Sunday, <<sundayAfterEffectiveDate>>. Federal law does not allow a Military UI claim to start before the separation date listed on the DD214. You must wait to submit your claim application until Sunday, <<sundayPriorEffectiveDate>>. {Militarydetails4/11}\n"
        },
        {
         "type": "panel",
         "name": "panel9",
         "elements": [
          {
           "type": "text",
           "name": "Military details 5/11",
           "tag": "Optimum Number",
           "title": "Please enter the number of days of accrued leave as it appears in item 16 on Form DD214",
           "isRequired": true
          },
          {
           "type": "dropdown",
           "name": "Military details 6/11",
           "tag": "Optimum Dropdown",
           "title": "What was the Character of Service? (Item 24)",
           "isRequired": true,
           "choices": [
            "Honorable",
            "Dishonorable",
            "General",
            "Other Than Honorable",
            "Uncharacterized",
            "Bad Conduct"
           ]
          },
          {
           "type": "radiogroup",
           "name": "Military details 7/11",
           "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
           "title": "Are there any dates of time lost listed in item #29 on your DD214?",
           "isRequired": true,
           "choices": [
            "Yes",
            "No"
           ]
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "name": "Military details 8/11",
           "visible": false,
           "visibleIf": "{Military details 7/11} = 'Yes'",
           "tag": "Optimum Label",
           "title": "Please enter the Start Date and End Date of time lost in item #29 on your DD214.",
           "placeHolder": "THIS IS NOT A QUESTION"
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "name": "Military details 8/11 Start Date",
           "visible": false,
           "visibleIf": "{Military details 7/11} = 'Yes'",
           "tag": "Optimum Date",
           "title": "Start Date",
           "isRequired": true
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "name": "Military details 8/11 End Date",
           "visible": false,
           "visibleIf": "{Military details 7/11} = 'Yes'",
           "tag": "Optimum Date",
           "title": "End Date",
           "isRequired": true
          },
          {
           "type": "radiogroup",
           "name": "Military details 9/11",
           "visible": false,
           "visibleIf": "{Military details 7/11} = 'No'",
           "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
           "title": "Have you had any other employment since your military service ended on {Militarydetails4/11}?",
           "description": "A monetary record is a document that displays your benefit amounts and information used to determine your benefit amounts, such as your earned wages, number of dependents you claimed, and employers you’ve worked for in the past 18 months.",
           "isRequired": true,
           "choices": [
            "Yes",
            "No"
           ]
          },
          {
           "type": "panel",
           "name": "panel10",
           "elements": [
            {
             "type": "html",
             "name": "question6",
             "html": "TODO: Change to [Invoke System Requirement 78038:  The system shall interface with O*Net to derive codes by job titles.]"
            },
            {
             "type": "text",
             "name": "Military details 10/11",
             "tag": "Optimum SingleLine",
             "title": "What was your job title?",
             "isRequired": true
            },
            {
             "type": "text",
             "name": "Military details 11/11",
             "tag": "Optimum SingleLine",
             "title": "What were your job duties?",
             "isRequired": true
            },
            {
             "type": "html",
             "name": "Military no wages msg",
             "html": "<a title=\"A monetary record is a document that displays your benefit amounts. This information is based on wages paid in the base period of your claim.\">Wages you earned from the military will not be listed on your first monetary record  because these wages must be requested. Once we receive your wages, we will send you a corrected monetary record.</a>"
            }
           ],
           "visible": false,
           "visibleIf": "{Military details 9/11} ='No'"
          }
         ],
         "visible": false,
         "visibleIf": "compareDate({Militarydetails4/11}, computeBYB()) < 0 or compareDate({Militarydetails4/11}, computeBYB()) = 0"
        }
       ],
       "visible": false,
       "visibleIf": "{Where are you?} = 'IA'"
      }
     ],
     "visible": false,
     "visibleIf": "{Military service} = 'Yes'"
    }
   ],
   "title": "Military Service",
   "category": "Military Service",
   "blockIf": "({Where are you?} notempty and {Where are you?} != 'IA') or (compareDate({Militarydetails4/11}, <<BYB>>) = 1)"
  },
  {
   "name": "Federal Civilian Employment",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "radiogroup",
     "name": "Federal work confirmation",
     "tag": "Optimum RadioGroup",
     "title": "Did you work for the Federal Government (not including military service) at any time after <<basePeriodBeginDate>>?",
     "isRequired": true,
     "choices": [
      "Yes",
      "No"
     ]
    },
    {
     "type": "panel",
     "name": "panel11",
     "elements": [
      {
       "type": "text",
       "name": "Federal work details 1/3",
       "tag": "Optimum SingleLine",
       "title": "What was the name of your Federal Employer?",
       "isRequired": true
      },
      {
       "type": "text",
       "name": "Federal work details 2/3",
       "tag": "Optimum SingleLine",
       "title": "In which department within the Federal Agency did you work?",
       "isRequired": true
      },
      {
       "type": "dropdown",
       "name": "Federal work details 3/3",
       "tag": "Optimum Dropdown",
       "title": "What was your Last Office Duty Station",
       "isRequired": true,
       "choices": [
        "item1",
        "item2",
        "item3"
       ],
       "choiceUrl": "/optimum-clientside-library/platform-services/dist/data/statesList.json"
      },
      {
       "type": "html",
       "name": "question10",
       "visibleIf": "{Federal work details 3/3} <> 'IA' and <<IowaBasePeriodWages>> = true and {Federal work details 3/3} notempty",
       "html": "You are not eligible to file a claim in Iowa. You must file a UI application in the state where you worked for the Federal Employer. View the contact information for your state here. Contact [name of state] at [phone number and URL]. "
      },
      {
       "type": "panel",
       "name": "panel12",
       "elements": [
        {
         "type": "multipletext",
         "name": "Federal work information 1/3",
         "tag": "Optimum Address",
         "title": "What is the payroll address from your SF8 or SF50 form?",
         "isRequired": true,
         "items": [
          {
           "name": "addressLine1"
          },
          {
           "name": "addressLine2"
          },
          {
           "name": "city"
          },
          {
           "name": "state"
          },
          {
           "name": "zip"
          },
